Package com.hhstechgroup.tests.regressionBaseline.vi_PEMEnrollment

This Package contains test classes covering all the test stories for PEM Enrollments.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PEMEnrollmentApproveTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get a submitted PEM and approves it.
    PEMEnrollmentDenyTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get a submitted PEM and deny it.
    PEMProviderAppealApprovalProcessTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get a denied PEM and appeals and approves it.
    PEMProviderAppealDenialProcessTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get a denied PEM and appeals and deny it.
    PEMProviderCocAddAffiliationTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get an approved PEM and adds an affiliation.
    PEMProviderCoCAndAppealDenialProcessTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get a Coc denied of a PEM provider and appeals and deny it.
    PEMProviderCocDenialProcessTest
    This method contains a test which uses a data provider to get an approved PEM and creates and denies an identifying information CoC
    PEMProviderCocEndAffiliationTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get an approved PEM and ends an affiliation.
    PEMProviderCocProcessTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get an approved PEM and creates and approves an alternate email change CoC.
    PEMProviderPreConditionSetupTest
    This test class sets the Systems Option configuration for PEM Provider.
    PEMProviderReactiveAndTerminationProviderTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get an active PEM and terminates and reactive.
    PEMProviderRegistrationAndSubmissionTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to register a new Provider and, creates and submits a PEM enrollment
    PEMProviderSuspendedAndReactivateProviderTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get an active PEM and suspends and reactive.
